{"tid":326504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭悼馬航MH17墜毀三周年","createTime":"2017-07-18T05:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T13:44:27.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2155785d92f346939ff81b9808a974ffc71f359","tid":326504,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】馬航MH17客機遭導彈擊落墜毀三周年，荷蘭舉行悼念儀式。<br />\n<br />\n儀式在荷蘭史基普機場附近一個紀念公園舉行，公園入面種了代表罹難人數的298棵樹，形成了一條絲帶的外型。2000多名罹難乘客家屬、荷蘭首相呂特和王室成員出席，為紀念碑揭幕，又讀出罹難者的姓名。<br />\n<br />\n三年前，馬航MH17的波音777客機在烏克蘭上空遭地對空導彈擊落墜毀，機上所有人全部死亡。罹難者來自17個國家，但有近200名荷蘭人。<br />\n<br />\n國際調查結果認為導彈是在親俄武裝分子控制的地區發射，導彈裝備則來自俄羅斯。俄羅斯否認涉及事件，認為結論存在政治偏見。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=228777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D228777&d=wxg8iiEDpLG4QBOT5BMfm10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ef033f5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D228777&h=ea1ce612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=228777</a>"},{"pid":"801802cd27cea320a572263bf1f6681e5defb6cd","tid":326504,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239602d8b40a9de6d168b2b516daafb6acf14137","tid":326504,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聲都唔夠膽出喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9dc0b5d5380e49844d0b6c2037b83f4a4961d7","tid":326504,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:44:27.000Z","msg":"家屬呢世都討不回公道"}]}